@node helppage1 " How to handle Multiview "
@toc help!

  @{b}How to handle Multiview@{ub}

  Using Multiview (or any other guide-shower) is easy. If you
  have found the way up to this page, I am sure that you know
  how to handle this utility. Anyway, here`s a small descrip-
  tion of the buttons you can click in the upper side.

  Contents   shows the Contents of the part of the guide where
             you are at the moment of clicking

  Index      loads the index part (productions, parties, system)

  Help       leads you to this text you are reading now

  Retrace    brings you back to the page which you have read before

  Browse <   leads your way back through the guide, i.e.
             shows the last node

  Browse >   leads your way on through the guide, i.e.
             shows the next node
@endnode

