@node helppage2-2 " The Meanings of the Short Forms of System-Information"
@toc helppage2



    @{b}The Meanings of the Short Forms of System-Information @{ub}


      AGA   new chipset system (A1200/A4000)
      ECS   enhanced chipset system
      OCS   original chipset system
      Inc.  Incorporated
      inc.  inclusive
      Ltd.  Limited
      Mem   Memory
      MT    multi-tasking
@endnode

!!!

@node helppage3 " Meanings of the Entries "
@toc help!

  @{b}The meanings of the Entries@{ub}


    [Name of the Production]

     Producer  : Name of the producing Group

     Coder     : Name of the Programmer
     Graphician: Name of the Graphician
     Sounder   : Name of the Musician
     Designer  : Name of the Designer, Ascii-Maker, Raytracer, a.s.o.
     Editor    : Name of the Main-Editor

     Size      : this is the size of the product in its form in the nets
     System    : lists up the configuration used by the production
                 (AGA, HD, Memory, Kickstart-version, OS-version);
                 HD-installable means that a HD is not required
                 (in opposition to a simple remark "HD")
     Secr. Part: explains what to do to reach the secret part
     How2Handle: describes how to use the demo (Relo, Exit, KillAga),
                 how to fix it or install it on harddisk, a.s.o.
     Remark    : anything else to be added

     Genre     : What is the Production exactly?
                 (Diskdemo, Filedemo, Intro, Sounddisk, Slideshow)
@endnode

