@node whatisit " What is <The Scene>? "
@toc information


  @{b}What is @{i}The Scene? @{ui}@{ub}


   This  guide  was  written  and  compiled for the purpose to unite all
   releases from the important Amiga-Scene-Parties into one list, mainly
   as a small orientation  for  everybody  who collects or searches  for
   special productions  or  for  productions  from special groups or who
   wants to gather information  (like hardware requirements, single pro-
   ducers or what so ever) about a special production. I hope this guide
   is helpful for at least some of you :)

   This guide does not include:
     - pack series (rarely own group`s file demos collections)
     - mag-parts of any pack series
     - any productions including nazi-propaganda
     - sounddisks just playing a module with no code and GFX
     - cheat disks, doc disks or solution disks
     - games or game-clones
     - tools or tool-clones
     - the most of those ugly hardcore demos and slideshows
     - various private module or slideshow collections
     - any stuff (PD-series) from commercial PD-distributors.

   Productions in this guide are only pure ...
     - file demos (dentros)
     - disk demos (megademos, trackmos)
     - intros
     - packmenu previews
     - diskmags
     - sounddisks
     - slideshows.

   I hope that you can find use for this guide and that you are thinking
   about @{"supporting me" link support} in the further development. Thanks in advance!
@endnode
